        <summary lang="en_GB">A quick way to install Add-on Repositories (Kodi 19 and up)</summary>
        <description lang="en_GB">Quickly and easily add third party sources to your File Manager, so you can install from zip file[CR]For Kodi 19 and above versions.[CR]None of the Repos are contained within this addon, it only serves to install URL's so you can download and install the developer's official repo zip file. [CR]This add-on is a fork of another add-on. The listing was updated and reformatted after some extensive searches for repositories and add-ons. Credit to the original creator for it's design and function. For info on add-ons in general, see https://www.reddit.com/r/Addons4Kodi/</description>
        <platform>all</platform>
        <language>en</language>
        <license>GPL-2.0-or-later</license>
        <assets>
            <icon>icon.png</icon>
            <fanart></fanart>
        </assets>
    </extension>
</addon>

